2.name: Limbo
description: You are floating in a formless void, detached from all sensation of physical
matter, surrounded by swirling glowing light, which fades into the relative
darkness around you without any trace of edges or shadow.
There is a "No Tipping" notice pinned to the darkness.

12.name: Level B2 On "The Highwind"
description: You are on the bottom level of "The High Wind".  Here is kind of a cargo
area.  To the west you see an iron door with the title "Chocobo Stable".  To
the east you see another iron door with the title "Operation", which is like
a meeting room/dining room.  You see a flight of stairs going up.

10.name: On The Deck Of The Highwind
description: You stand on a large desk.  Above you the massive airship looms as you
hear the sound of the engines running.  The deck gives you a good view of
all the surroundings, since it is located towards the bottom.  You see a
door that leads to the stairs going down.

13.name: Operation
description: You stand in a large room.  A large square table sits in the middle of
the floor, with 12 chairs around it.  You see a large map of the surrounding
areas behind the main chair.  A large long light hangs from above.

description: You walk along the Halls of Wisdom.  To either side of you, a large
door stands, leading into another, secret room.  To the north, you see
ROOM [1], The Limbo.  To the south, you see ROOM [2], The Linkdead

4.name: Freezer
description: You stand in a deep dark freezer. You try to move, but yet...you
can't. You feel nothing, all there is your mind. You see
other mortals in here, standing in place. You have been frozen
and placed in the Mortal Freezer. Have Fun.

27.name: The Halls Of Wisdom
description: You walk along the Halls of Wisdom.  To either side of you, a large
door stands, leading into another, secret room.  To the north, you see
ROOM [3], The Corner.  To the south, you see ROOM [4], The Freezer.

72.name: {&T{*he {&C{*ourt {&O{*f {BWa{bt{*e{wr{*d{be{Bep {RJu{rsti{Rce{x
description: You stand in a large court room, cut from the very rock that makes
the core of the planet.  The ceiling is smooth grante, with lights
hanging down from wires, glowing brightly.  Rows of benchs strech
towards the west, towards a large wood Judge desk, and the witness
stand.  On the walls, small alcoves cut into the stone walls, and a
statue of each god stands, Cyric, Nisstyre, Talos, Teron, Selune,
Tempus, Moradin, Kossuth, and Hanali.  You are here for justice, and
justice only.

34.name: The Hallway Of Immortals
description: [Selune: EAST] [Mielikki: WEST]

31.name: The Center Chamber
description: You stand in the center chamber, a large cavernous opening going to
the peek of the mountain.  The hallway splits up into two sections,
north and south.  To the north, you see the personal chambers of the
gods, and immortals.  To the south, you see a large iron door, leading
into some kind of room.  To the east, you see the doors to the office
of Nisstyre Bloodstoner.

11.name: Level B1 On "The High Wind"
description: You are on the middle level of "The High Wind".  You see a pair of large
doors to the north, which look to be the cargo doors.  A flight of stairs
goes either up or down.  Up is to the observation deck, and down is to the
Flight Control Deck.

15.name: Control Deck
description: Welcome to the control deck of the Highwind.  Here you see two posts
where controls to all the engines and a large wheel sits.  This is the
master control of the great airship.  Ahead of all of this is a large dome
window, looking out into the lands.  From here the view is awesome.

6.name: Pool Room
description: You stand in a large room.  A glowing pool sits in the middle of the
room.  The Rest Of The Room Is empty.
==IF YOU ARE IN THIS ROOM AN IMPLEMENTOR HAS LOADED YOUR CHARACTER==

7.name: Battle Arena
description: You stand in a circular arena with weapons of all types attached to
the wall all over.  Blood stains the ground and the stench of the
dead fills your nostrils with every breath.  Only the strong shall
survive this battle and the weak slaughtered and left to rot.

21.name: The P-Vault Loading Room
description: NOTICE!!!!
If you find yourself in this room, then that means you are still appart
of Waterdeep's Player Vault aka P-Vault, which is used to save characters
during our maintance pfile cleanups. If you are currently playing or plan
on begin to play, please write a note to Nisstyre just with the subject
as "remove me from the pvault".
{x
This is currently Pfile Clean up done on: July 6th 2001 3:25am.
Next Pfile Clean Up will be done on: August 6th 2001.

40.name: The Arena Locker Room
description: You stand inside a large circular shaped room, lined with many
lockers and various weapons that are used by the masters of several
fighting styles.  In the center of this room stands a few wooden
benches and a weight bench for the competitors to utilize while they
wait to enter the fight.

30.name: The Halls Of Wisdom
description: You walk along the Halls of Wisdom.  To either side of you, a large
door stands, leading into another, secret room.  To the north, you see
ROOM [22], The De-Clanning Room.  To the south, you see ROOM [24], The
Seventh Layer Of Hell.

24.name: The Seventh Layer Of Hell
description: You stand amounst fire and brimestone.  Torutured souls slave away,
dragging large bolders, and being whipped by a demon.  Flames burn
everywhere, and molten earth flows around, like a large river.
Welcome to hell, mother fucker.

14.name: Chocobo Stables
description: You stand in a bare part of the ship.  Here you see the room has been
made into a Stable.  On the north wall a fence has been made to hold some
live stock.  A chair sits against the west wall for the stable keepers.
Bags of grain lie on the floor.

32.name: The Hallway Of Immortals
description: [Hanali: WEST] [Moradin: EAST]

29.name: The Halls Of Wisdom
description: You walk along the Halls of Wisdom.  To either side of you, a large
door stands, leading into another, secret room.  To the north, you see
ROOM [20], The Mortal Interigation Room.  To the south, you see ROOM
[21], The Pvault Loading Room.

8.name: Arena Stadium
description: A thunderous roar fills the stadium as you clamber to find your seat and
witness the upcoming arena match.  You see bloodstains on the very front
benches from particularly gruesome matches of the past, and you try to find
a clean patch of bench and get comfortable.  For whom will you cheer to
reign victorious over the corpse of his fallen opponent?

17.name: Storage room
description: This room is for storage and counters, if you are here, leave.

28.name: The Halls Of Wisdom
description: You walk along the Halls of Wisdom.  To either side of you, a large
door stands, leading into another, secret room.  To the north, you see
ROOM [5], The Endless Void.  To the south, you see ROOM [6], The
Immortal Pfile Loading Room.

22.name: The DE-Clanning Room
description: ATTENTION!
If you are reading this, then the leaders of your clan has
requested the immortal staff to have you removed in a mass
wipe of members of the clan you where in. Any questions about
why, approach your leaders, not the immortals.

3.name: Corner
description: You are standing with your nose in the corner.  Every time you try to
turn around, you get slapped upside the head and quickly resume your
position.

73.name: Floating...
description: You are floating...

16.name: Cabin Chambers
description: You stand in a large bedroom aboard the ship.  Round port hole windows
look out to the east overlooking the skies and any other sight in here.  You
see a large feather bed, with a table next to it against one wall.  A desk
sits on the western wall and a map hangs from above it.

20.name: The {RInterrogation {xRoom{x
description: You stand in a bare room.  Nothing is in here.  The walls are gray, and
only a single door leads out.  A table sits in the middle of the room.  Only
4 chairs sit next to the table.  That is all.

25.name: The Immortal Lounge
description: You step into a large lounge, filled with all kinds of diffrent,
interesting furniture.  A large window looks out over the mountain
side, and below the small city of Westbridge can be seen.  The lounge
is filled with tables, couches and chairs.  A large bar stretches
along one wall, with a jukebox on the end.  A pair of large doors lead
east.

33.name: The Hallway Of Immortals
description: [Tempus: WEST] [Kossuth: EAST]

23.name: Player Loading Room - DUP EQ CASE
description: {x{RATTENTION!!!  {x If you find yourself frozen and in this room, this
means that you have been found with more than 100 peices of duplicated
EQ on your character(s).  We have created a program that allows us to
process every pfile from the mud, and tells us your address, alts and
duplicated EQ.  Unless you have a really good excuse, the character
that is room will likely be destroyed.  Talk to NISSTYRE, TYR or
MORADIN about the character.  If you are guilty, then do the right
thing and delete.
